'''2005年吉布提总统选举'''于2005年4月8日举行，[[吉布提|吉布提]]在职[[吉布提国家元首列表|总统]][[伊斯梅尔·奥马尔·盖莱|伊斯梅尔·奥马尔·盖莱]]在没有竞争者的情形下当选，开始一个新的6年[[任期制|任期]]。

==背景==
[[哈桑·古莱德·阿普蒂敦|哈桑·古莱德·阿普蒂敦]]自吉布提1977年独立以来担任总统，直到1999年下台。阿普蒂敦在国际社会压力下，1992年实行[[多党制|多党制]]，<ref name=kicks>{{cite web | url = http://www.irinnews.org/report.aspx?reportid=53628 | title = DJIBOUTI: No challengers for Guelleh as presidential campaign kicks off | accessdate = 2009-02-20 | date = 2005-03-29 | publisher = ''[[IRIN|IRIN]]'' | archive-date = 2008-02-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080225120215/http://www.irinnews.org/Report.aspx?ReportId=53628 | dead-url = no }}</ref>在{{link-en|1999年吉布提总统选举|Djiboutian presidential election, 1999}}中，阿普蒂敦的外甥伊斯梅尔·奥马尔·盖莱以74%的得票率当选。<ref name=elections>{{cite web | url = http://africanelections.tripod.com/dj.html | title = Elections in Djibouti | accessdate = 2009-02-20 | publisher = ''African Elections Database'' | archive-date = 2017-01-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170102105012/http://africanelections.tripod.com/dj.html | dead-url = no }}</ref> {{link-en|2003年吉布提议会选举|Djiboutian parliamentary election, 2003}}中，盖莱领导的{{link-en|总统多数联盟|Union for the Presidential Majority (Djibouti)}}包揽了所有65个席位，反对派指责[[选举操控手法|选举舞弊]]。<ref name=kicks/><ref name=uncontested>{{cite web | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2005/04/09/international/africa/09djibouti.html?pagewanted=print&position= | title = Djibouti's Leader Wins Uncontested Vote | accessdate = 2009-02-20 | date = 2005-04-09 | publisher = ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'' | archive-date = 2014-04-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140427012335/http://www.nytimes.com/2005/04/09/international/africa/09djibouti.html?pagewanted=print&position= | dead-url = no }}</ref>

==竞选==
吉布提主要反对党没有提出总统候选人，呼吁支持者抵制这次选举<ref name=kicks/>。{{link-en|穆罕默德·达乌德·谢海姆|Mohamed Daoud Chehem}}是唯一宣称要参加选举的反对派候选人，但是在2005年3月10日，他退出选举，理由是没有足够资金参与选举。<ref name=clear>{{cite web| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/4337003.stm | title = Clear run for Djibouti's leader | accessdate = 2009-02-19 | date = 2005-03-10 | publisher = ''[[BBC_Online|BBC Online]]''}}</ref> 3月18日，反对党{{link-en|恢復團結和民主陣線|Front for the Restoration of Unity and Democracy}}发表声明说“通过投票箱改变吉布提共和国基本是死路一条”。<ref name=kicks/>

尽管没有竞选对手，盖莱仍然进行了颇有声势的竞选活动。他举行了多次晚间竞选集会，许诺减少[[贫困|贫困]]、提高[[妇女权利|妇女权利]]和改善政府的透明度。他批评反对派不敢跟他竞争，他称他对于没有竞选对手感到遗憾。<ref name=leader>{{cite web | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/4421515.stm | title = Djibouti leader wins one-man poll | accessdate = 2009-02-19 | date = 2005-04-09 | publisher = ''[[BBC_Online|BBC Online]]'' | archive-date = 2019-08-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190821174522/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/4421515.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=violence>{{cite web | url = http://www.arabnews.com/?page=1&section=0&article=61839&d=9&m=4&y=2005&pix=kingdom.jpg&category=Kingdom | title = Violence Mars Voting in Djibouti | accessdate = 2009-02-20 | date = 2005-04-09 | publisher = ''[[ArabNews|ArabNews]]'' | archive-date = 2014-04-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140427010309/http://www.arabnews.com/?page=1&section=0&article=61839&d=9&m=4&y=2005&pix=kingdom.jpg&category=Kingdom | dead-url = no }}</ref>

在投票日，发生了反对这次选举的抗议活动，警察喷射了[[催泪瓦斯|催泪瓦斯]]予以镇压<ref name=leader/>。吉布提官方[[通讯社|通讯社]]报道，这次选举[[投票率|投票率]]高达70%以上，但是反对派质疑这一数字的正确性<ref name=incumbent>{{cite web | url = http://www.afrol.com/articles/16113 | title = Djibouti incumbent wins one-man poll | accessdate = 2009-02-20 | date = 2005-04-12 | publisher = ''[[afrol|afrol]]'' | archive-date = 2008-08-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080830094338/http://www.afrol.com/articles/16113 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

