==余波==
伊斯梅尔·奥马尔·盖莱在2005年5月9日宣誓就任总统，开始自己的第二个任期，许诺促进吉布提[[经济发展|经济发展]]<ref name=sworn>{{cite web | url = http://www.irinnews.org/report.aspx?reportid=54297 | title = DJIBOUTI: Guelleh sworn in for second presidential term | accessdate = 2009-02-20 | date = 2005-05-09 | publisher = ''[[IRIN|IRIN]]'' | archive-date = 2008-12-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081227034003/http://www.irinnews.org/report.aspx?reportid=54297 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

